- Imperial soldiers: Wary distrust due to current political tensions in Skyrim
- Merchants: Transactional relationships focused on trading for better equipment
{% endblock %}

{% block occupation %}Warrior-for-hire who takes on contracts requiring combat skills, from escort missions to clearing bandit camps.{% endblock %}

{% block skills %}
